| --------- | -------------------- | ------------ |
| `INT`     | Integer number       | 25           |
| `VARCHAR` | Variable-length text | "Alice"      |
| `DATE`    | Date value           | 2025-08-10   |
| `BOOLEAN` | True or False value  | TRUE / FALSE |
